    "description": {
        "full": "Immerse yourself in this addictive puzzler that's all about strategically twisting and connecting mismatched dials to save precious droplitz.  Just making a single junction is child's play; can you master the art of the combo or will you let your pipes runneth over?  Be warned: losing too many droplitz can be hazardous to your ability to win.  With four unique play modes, a variety of board sizes, and infinite replayability, Droplitz promises to drain all your time away. There are no refunds for this item. For more information, see www.xbox.com/live/accounts.",
        "short": "Rotate dials to create paths to let the Droplitz flow and earn high scores!  Play over four different addictive modes - Classic, Zendurance, Power Up, and Infection.  Ever-increasing speeds and larger boards ensure you'll always have a challenge ahead!  Show everyone you're the best with online Leaderboards and Achievements."
    },
